<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='519000' id='t-519000'>I'm a witness, and I want my testimony to be honest and uncensored.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='526000' id='t-526000'>I also want it to be powerful and eloquent,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='529000' id='t-529000'>and to do as much justice as possible</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='531000' id='t-531000'>to the experience of the people I'm photographing.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='534000' id='t-534000'>This man was in an NGO feeding center,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='537000' id='t-537000'>being helped as much as he could be helped.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='539000' id='t-539000'>He literally had nothing. He was a virtual skeleton,</span>
