<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='578000' id='t-578000'>This man had just been liberated from a Hutu death camp.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='582000' id='t-582000'>He allowed me to photograph him for quite a long time,</span>
