<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='824000' id='t-824000'>These heroin addicts in detox in Pakistan</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='827000' id='t-827000'>reminded me of figures in a play by Beckett:</span>
